ruby-cucumber-core (1.5.0-2) unstable; urgency=medium

  [ Utkarsh Gupta ]
  * Add salsa-ci.yml

  [ Debian Janitor ]
  * Use secure copyright file specification URI.
  * Use secure URI in debian/watch.
  * Set debhelper-compat version in Build-Depends.
  * Set upstream metadata fields: Bug-Database, Bug-Submit, Repository,
    Repository-Browse.
  * Update Vcs-* headers from URL redirect.
  * Use canonical URL in Vcs-Git.

  [ Cédric Boutillier ]
  * Add patch to load GFM parser for kramdown in specs
  * Add explicit build-dependency on ruby-kramdown-parser-gfm to prepare for
    kramdown v2
  * Bump dephelper compat level to 13
  * Bump Standards-Version to 4.5.0 (no changes needed)
  * Set Rules-Requires-Root to no
  * Move debian/watch to gemwatch.debian.net

